| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1565 — Recovery Inhibition (embargo)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 39d8cd61-8768-5eb9-8926-dbb5aa4f574e"
